SELECT patient_name, test_date, result_units FROM patient_demographics JOIN test_results ON patient_demographics.patient_id = test_results.patient_id

### TABLEDATA

CREATE TABLE Patient (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name TEXT,
  age INT,
  gender TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Test (
  test_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  test_name TEXT,
  test_description TEXT,
  test_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE TestResult (
  result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  test_id INT REFERENCES Test(test_id),
  patient_id INT REFERENCES Patient(patient_id),
  result_value FLOAT,
  result_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE TrendAnalysis (
  analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  result_id INT REFERENCES TestResult(result_id),
  trend_value FLOAT,
  trend_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE TreatmentPlan (
  plan_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  analysis_id INT REFERENCES TrendAnalysis(analysis_id),
  plan_description TEXT,
  plan_date TIMESTAMP
);
